Package: ChebyshevMax
Type: Package
Title: Curve Fitting and Extreme Value Search with Chebyshev Polynomials
Version: 0.9.9
Authors@R: as.person(c(
  "Sebastian Kiefer <s.kiefer@posteo.de> [aut, cre]", 
  "Andreas Hense [ths]"))
Description: The aim of this package is to fit a chebyshev polynomial of order n
    to a arbitrary data series using least squares, to derive the curve and 
    calculate its roots. So one can find the multiple extrema of the data series.
Imports:
    rootSolve
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: TRUE
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests: testthat
